<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="21Feb1935"><font color="red">21 February 1935</font> <i>NLPK</i> (from Paul L&eacute;on to J. Ralph Pinker): the new fragment which is to appear in the next issue of Transition is not of a kind to be published separately &mdash; it will be the beginning and end of a section of the second part. </div>
